本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:魏明珠研究生(外文):Ming-chu Wei論文名稱:中小企業人力資源招募與甄選方法及成效之研究-以北區資訊電子工業為例論文名稱(外文):A Study of Human Resources Recruitment,Selection Methods,and Performance of Small and Medium Enterprises－An Example of Electronics Industry in Northern Taiwan指導教授:衛民學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立中正大學系所名稱:勞工所學門:社會及行為科學學門學類:綜合社會及行為科學學類論文出版年:2008畢業學年度:97語文別:中文論文頁數:213中文關鍵詞:中小企業、招募、甄選、方法、成效外文關鍵詞:selection、small and medium businesses、recruitment、methods、performance相關次數:

被引用:15點閱:2083評分:下載:302書目收藏:0



人才的招募甄選作業是一切人力資源管理的開始，亦是人力資源部門為企業提供人力資源的弁鄐仇怑滬n且重視的工作。過去國內有關人力資源招募甄選的主題在不同的產業上分別有相關的學術研究報告，但以中小企業作為主要深入研究對象者之學術性報告尚屬少數。本研究主要針對中小企業人力資源「招募」及「甄選」的方法及其成效進行深入探討。      本研究透過文獻分析法及以深度訪談法，針對北區資訊電子工業八家中小企業個案分析，結果發現：一、在專業職、業務職、行政職、中高階管理職不同的四種職務上所採用的招募方法中，專業職、業務職以及行政職人員皆以人力銀行網站為主，其次為員工/親友推薦；中高階管理職人員以員工/親友推薦為主，其次為同業推薦及獵人頭。二、在招募方法成效上，專業職、業務職以及行政職人員皆以人力銀行網站及員工/親友推薦成效較佳；中高階管理職人員以員工/親友推薦及使用獵人頭較佳。三、在專業職、業務職、行政職、中高階管理職不同的四種職務上所採用的甄選方法中，專業職、業務職以及行政職人員皆履歷表審核、面談為主，其次為雇用測驗；中高階管理職人員以面談為主、其次為背景查核。四、在甄選方法成效上，不同的四種職務專業職、業務職、行政職以及中高階管理職人員皆以面談成效最佳。      本研究最後針對研究結果提出建議：中小企業在進行招募及甄選實務作業的現況、所面臨的困境以及採取的因應對策方面，建議加強人資人員專業知識，並設計符合組織之制式流程；改善影響招募甄選人才的因素，降低流動率；提升競爭力，加強公司制度以及落實人力資源管理，吸引並留住人才。有關招募方面建議進行招募員工時，優先考慮人力銀行網站與員工/親友推薦方法，制定完善的員工/親友推薦獎勵方案，以及增加進用符合工作職務特性之身心障礙求職者。有關甄選方面建議增加主管的面談技巧訓練，以及增加不同測驗的甄選工具並且標準化。

Recruitment and selection of talents is the beginning of all human resources management and the primary as well most valued job in human resources department at enterprises.  One can find academic reports on different domestic industries of recruitment and selection of talents, there are few academic reports focusing on small and medium businesses.  This research aims at in-depth exploration of methods and performance of recruitment and selection of talents of small and medium businesses.      Through literature analysis and in-depth interviews, the researcher conducts practical analysis of 8 small and medium businesses of electronics industry in northern taiwan and finds:1.Main method for recruitment of professional, sales and administration talents is human resources websites, followed by recommendation by employees/friends; that of medium/high ranking talents is recommendation by employees/friends, followed by recommendation by competitors and headhunters.2.In performance, human resources websites and recommendation by employees/friends have better performance on professional, sales and administration talents recruitment; recommendation by employees/friends and headhunters yield better results for medium/high ranking talents.3.Main methods of selection for professional, sales and administration talents are review of resumes and interviews, followed by employment tests; those of medium/high ranking talents are mainly interviews, followed by background review.4.In selection, interviews have best results on the four kinds of posts.      Suggestions are provided at the end of the paper—enhancement of professional knowledge of human resources personnel, design of suitable system procedures for the organization, improving factors affecting recruitment and selection, reducing flow rate, enhancing competence, strengthening company system, enforcement of HR management to attract and keep talents on recruitment and selection.  As for recruitment, human resources websites and recommendation by employees/friends are preferred. Comprehensive program on encouragement of recommendation by employees/friends has to be established; recruiting more physically disabled that meet the requirements of jobs is also needed.  On selection, interview skills of supervisors have to be improved; selection tools have to be more diverse and standardized.

